name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ChatGPT YouTube Video Summarizer, Transcript, Main points using AI ChatGPT

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ChatGPT YouTube video Summarizer, Main points, Transcript using ChatGPT to generate YouTube videos summary & Transcript in one click

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Generate YouTube video summary, Transcript and main points powered by ChatGPT, AI Assistant in one click. Summaries any Podcast or document 
No need to watch the whole video, one click to get a summary, transcript, and main points

we are using ChatGPT AI to generate the summary, Transcript & main points 

In just opening the extension you will get:

- A YouTube video summary in a single paragraph. 
- Digest the main points with bullet-point summaries.
- Download the YouTube video transcript
- copy the YouTube video summary to the clipboard to re-use it 
- added the option that embeds the extension into YouTube, so no need to click on the extension to open it

FAQ: 
What is the extension about :
GPT YouTube Video Summarizer, Transcript, Main points using AI ChatGPT, is a Chrome extension that generates a summary, main points, and a transcription for a YouTube video, any video can work

Do I need a ChatGPT account to run this extension? 
Nope,  we are using ChatGPT in the background

Does it only work for YouTube? 
That is correct, but we can extend that. If you have any requests, please add it in the support tab. 

How can I request adding a new language? 
Please request the new language from the support tab and we will try to prioritize it. 

Please if you have any questions feel free, to contact us support@summarizemyvideo.com
